{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the Gemini TTS integration and wrote the required reviewer summary to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/73_gemini_tts_integration/summary.md). The backend now h...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_196", "text": "Implemented the Gemini TTS integration and wrote the required reviewer summary to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/73_gemini_tts_integration/summary.md).\n\nThe backend now has a provider-isolated Gemini TTS adapter, a durable `AudioJobService` runtime path, config-driven TTS model selection, worker-side audio job execution, and durable failure handling. I verified it with targeted tests, broader regressions, and the full backend suite; the summary file includes the exact commands and results, the eval criteria, the architectural rationale, the key limitations, and the checkpoint commit `bef54ac43801e85c91f705c1881151ba56407bc0`.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 414, "prompt_index": 74, "prompt_name": "73 \u2014 Gemini TTS Integration", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T15:25:17-07:00"}
